this is a link to install the script as an .exe file.
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1buUF3seNO8VsL2mLUF8Cf8B_74DnIYpC?usp=sharing
there is a zip of the folder that includes the .exe + all it needs to run.
there is also a .msi installation file to install as .exe + create desktop shortcut.
the same .msi can be later used to uninstall.
this is the best option if you don't have python installed on your computer.
